lood of Internet traffic.\\nRisk - Absence of DDOS protection may lead to compromised systems and disruption in services.\\nRecommendation - DDOS protection should be configured properly to prevent external attacks on internal systems.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 11.2.2<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - PR.PT.5<br>\\nPCI DSS - RM11.6<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 18-7<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI03.07\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"6\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"SH.4.4.1c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"SH.4.4.2\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"What level of DDOS has been configured?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - A distributed denial-of-service (DDoS) attack is a malicious attempt to disrupt the normal traffic of a targeted server, service or network by overwhelming the target or its surrounding infrastructure with a flood of Internet traffic.\\nRisk - Absence of DDOS protection may lead to compromised systems and disruption in services.\\nRecommendation - DDOS protection should be configured properly to prevent external attacks on internal systems.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - <br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - <br>\\nPCI DSS - <br>\\nCIS Top 20 - <br>\\nCOBIT 5 - \",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Application 