isible to anyone in the organization within any administration modules.\\nRisk - Visible password can lead to compromise of credentials and unauthorized access.\\nRecommendation - Passwords should be encrypted white stored to prevent unauthorized access.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.2.1<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - PR.AC.6<br>\\nPCI DSS - AC8.1<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 4-4<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - Not Applicable\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"3\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"ID.5.3.7c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"ID.5.3.8\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Does the systems/platform operate in a mixed authentication mode (i.e. external and local authentication)?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - Passwords\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.2.1<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - PR.AC.6<br>\\nPCI DSS - AC8.1<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 4-4<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - Not Applicable\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"3\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"ID.5.3.8c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"ID.5.3.9\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Are audit logs available that include AT LEAST all of the following; login, logout, actions performed, and source IP address?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - Audit logs should include the basic information to be available for a review and to support forensics.\\nRisk - Logs stored within the application could be tampered with which could lead to audit trails for user activity being unavailable in the event of a security incident\\nRecommendation - Application logs should be sent to a centralized log management system (SIEM)\\n\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.2.5<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - PR.PT.1<br>\\nPCI DSS - VM5.2<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 1-3<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI08.05\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"3\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"ID.5.3.9c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    }\n   ],\n   \"title\": \"Authentication\"\n  }\n ],\n \"showQuestionNumbers\": \"off\",\n \"questionDescriptionLocation\": \"underInput\"\n}', '2021-02-04', 0, 15, '2020-12-09 14:44: