(113, 'Availability', '{\n \"title\": \"AVAILABILITY\",\n \"pages\": [\n  {\n   \"name\": \"BUSINESS CONTINUITY\",\n   \"elements\": [\n    {\n     \"type\": \"html\",\n     \"name\": \"Description\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n     \"html\": \"<h6>ISF SoGP BC1.1 Business Continuity Strategy</h6>\\n<b>Principle:</b> A business continuity strategy covering the whole organisation should be established, which promotes the need for business continuity management, embeds business continuity management into the organisation\'s culture, and is implemented in the form of a business continuity programme.</br>\\n<b>Objective:</b> To align business continuity goals with the organisation\'s business goals, provide resilience against disruption and minimise impact to the organisation in the event of a disaster or emergency.\"\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"html\",\n     \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"html\": \"<h6>Associated Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 14.2.3<br>\\nNIST - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - Not Applicable<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - DSS04.01\"\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"text\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.1\",\n     \"title\": \"Who is the owner responsible for the maintenance and review of the Business Continuity Plan (BCP)?\",\n     \"description\": \"For information purposes to identify Ownership.\"\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.1c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.2\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Are specific crisis management roles and responsibilities defined and documented?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - All roles involved with the management of a crisis should be defined and documented. \\nRisk - Confusion over the roles and responsibilities can effect the efficiency and effectiveness of a recovery.\\nRecommendation - Ensure \\\"All\\\" roles required to participate defined, documented and shared with the participants.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 14.2.3<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - Not Applicable<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - DSS04.01\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"All Roles\",\n       \"text\": \"All Roles\",\n       \"Score\": \"4\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Most Roles\",\n       \"text\": \"Most Roles\",\n       \"Score\": \"3\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Acceptable\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Some Roles\",\n       \"text\": \"Some Roles\",\n       \"Score\": \"2\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.2c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.3\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Have you provided a reference to your BCP? Add link to comments field or send file to Security Project Manager.\",\n     \"description\": \"The document provided will be reviewed for the completeness and advice will be given where necessary.  \",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 14.2.3<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - Not Applicable<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - DSS04.01\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"4\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.3c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"html\",\n     \"name\": \"Description\",\n     \"visible\": false,\n     \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n     \"html\": \"<h6>ISF SoGP BC2.1 Business Continuity Planning</h6>\\n<b>Principle:</b> Business continuity plans should be developed and documented to support critical business processes throughout the organisation.</br>\\n<b>Objective:</b> To provide relevant individuals with a documented set of actions to perform in the event of a disaster or emergency affecting business applications and technical infrastructure, enabling critical business processes to be resumed within agreed timescales.\"\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"html\",\n     \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n     \"visible\": false,\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"html\": \"<h6>Associated Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 12.2.1<br>\\nNIST - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 19-8<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI07.06\"\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.4\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Is there a defined problem/issue escalation plan in your BCP for impacted clients?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - Plans shall be developed and implemented to maintain or restore operations and ensure availability of information at the required level and in the required time scales following interruption to, or failure of, critical business processes.\\nRisk - Without business continuity plans, teams will not be able to limit losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations which could result in inefficient and ineffective recovery.\\nRecommendation - Documented business continuity plans should be in place which could be followed in order to mitigate losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations and to enable efficient and effective recovery.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 12.2.1<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 19-8<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI07.06\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"4\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.4c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.5\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Is there a documented communication plan in your BCP for impacted clients?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - Plans shall be developed and implemented to maintain or restore operations and ensure availability of information at the required level and in the required time scales following interruption to, or failure of, critical business processes.\\nRisk - Without business continuity plans, teams will not be able to limit losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations which could result in inefficient and ineffective recovery.\\nRecommendation - Documented business continuity plans should be in place which could be followed in order to mitigate losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations and to enable efficient and effective recovery.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 12.2.1<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 19-8<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI07.06\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Yes\",\n       \"text\": \"Yes\",\n       \"Score\": \"4\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"No\",\n       \"text\": \"No\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.5c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.6\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"How often are the components of the BCP reviewed and updated as needed to reflect change?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - Plans shall be developed and implemented to maintain or restore operations and ensure availability of information at the required level and in the required time scales following interruption to, or failure of, critical business processes.\\nRisk - Without business continuity plans, teams will not be able to limit losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations which could result in inefficient and ineffective recovery.\\nRecommendation - Documented business continuity plans should be in place which could be followed in order to mitigate losses caused by disruptions to critical business operations and to enable efficient and effective recovery.\",\n     \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n     \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks</h6>\\nISO/IEC 27002:2013 - 12.2.1<br>\\nNIST Cybersecurity Framework - Not Applicable<br>\\nPCI DSS - Not Applicable<br>\\nCIS Top 20 - CSC 19-8<br>\\nCOBIT 5 - BAI07.06\",\n     \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n     \"choices\": [\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Annually\",\n       \"text\": \"Annually\",\n       \"Score\": \"4\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Ad hoc (less often than annually)\",\n       \"text\": \"Ad hoc (less often than annually)\",\n       \"Score\": \"2\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      },\n      {\n       \"value\": \"Not sure\",\n       \"text\": \"Not sure\",\n       \"Score\": \"0\",\n       \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n      }\n     ]\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"comment\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.6c\",\n     \"width\": \"250px\",\n     \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n     \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Comment\",\n     \"hideNumber\": true,\n     \"cols\": 40\n    },\n    {\n     \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n     \"name\": \"AV.6.1.7\",\n     \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n     \"title\": \"Is there a maintained inventory of mission critical business resources?\",\n     \"description\": \"Statement - An inventory of mission critical business resources ensures correct coverage of plans should an interruption occur. \\nRisk - Without a full picture of the 