\": \"Description\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>SA1.4 Access Control Mechanisms \\u2013 Password<\\/h6><b>Principle:<\\/b> Target environments (e.g. business applications, systems or network devices) that are configured with access control mechanisms based on passwords, should require users to provide a valid User ID and password before they can gain access to them.<\\/br><b>Objective:<\\/b> To prevent unauthorised users from gaining access to password-protected critical or sensitive information, business applications, information systems, networks or computing devices.\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n                    \"width\": \"250px\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n                    \"hideNumber\": true,\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>Associated Frameworks<\\/h6>ISO\\/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.2.1<br>NIST - PR.AC.6<br>PCI DSS - AC8.1<br>CIS Top 20 - CSC 4-4<br>COBIT 5 - Not Applicable\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n                    \"name\": \"ID.5.3.9\",\n                    \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n                    \"title\": \"Are audit logs available that include AT LEAST all of the following; login, logout, actions performed, and source IP address?\",\n                    \"description\": \"Statement - Audit logs should include the basic information to be available for a review and to support forensics.Risk - Logs stored within the application could be tampered with which could lead to audit trails for user activity being unavailable in the event of a security incidentRecommendation - Application logs should be sent to a centralized log management system (SIEM)\",\n                    \"descriptionLocation\": \"underInput\",\n                    \"Framework\": \"<h6>Frameworks<\\/h6>ISO\\/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.2.5<br>NIST Cybersecurity Framework - PR.PT.1<br>PCI DSS - VM5.2<br>CIS Top 20 - CSC 1-3<br>COBIT 5 - BAI08.05\",\n                    \"commentText\": \"enter here\",\n                    \"choices\": [\n                        {\n                            \"value\": \"Yes\",\n                            \"text\": \"Yes\",\n                            \"Score\": \"3\",\n                            \"Standard\": \"Ideal\"\n                        },\n                        {\n                            \"value\": \"No\",\n                            \"text\": \"No\",\n                            \"Score\": \"0\",\n                            \"Standard\": \"Non-Standard\"\n                        }\n                    ]\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"comment\",\n                    \"name\": \"ID.5.3.9c\",\n                    \"width\": \"250px\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n                    \"title\": \"Comment\",\n                    \"hideNumber\": true,\n                    \"cols\": 40\n                }\n            ]\n        }\n    ]\n}', '2021-02-10 02:45:54', '2021-02-10 02:45:54');
