Access\",\n            \"elements\": [\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Description\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>SA1.3 Access Control Mechanisms<\\/h6><b>Principle:<\\/b> Access to business applications, systems, networks and computing devices should be restricted to authorised individuals by the use of access control mechanisms.<\\/br><b>Objective:<\\/b> To limit access to only authorised individuals.\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n                    \"width\": \"250px\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n                    \"hideNumber\": true,\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>Associated Frameworks<\\/h6>ISO\\/IEC 27002:2013 - 9.1.1<br>NIST - PR.AC.6<br>PCI DSS - BM2.2<br>CIS Top 20 - CSC 4-4<br>COBIT 5 - DSS05.02\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"radiogroup\",\n                    \"name\": \"ID.5.2.3\",\n                    \"useDisplayValuesInTitle\": false,\n                    \"title\": \"How are Joiners Movers Leavers processed?\",\n                    \"description\": \"Statement - There shall be\\u00a0a formal documented and implemented user registration and de-registration procedure for granting and revoking access.Risk - Without an access management process, business requirements for access to information technology systems may not be defined and documented, and access may not be provisioned in compliance with applicable laws, regulations, and policies.Recommendation - \\\"Documented access control procedures should be put in place covering the process for - employee onboarding- changes to an employees role- employee termination\\\"\",\n            