                  \"name\": \"Description\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>ISF SoGP PM2.3 Security Education\\/Training<\\/h6><b>Principle:<\\/b> Individuals should be educated\\/trained in how to run systems and applications correctly and how to develop and apply information security controls.<\\/br><b>Objective:<\\/b> To provide individuals with the skills required to protect information and systems effectively and fulfil their information security responsibilities.\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n                    \"width\": \"250px\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"startWithNewLine\": false,\n                    \"hideNumber\": true,\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>Associated Frameworks<\\/h6>ISO\\/IEC 27002:2013 - 5.1.1<br>NIST - PR.AT.1<br>PCI DSS - BM1.5<br>CIS Top 20 - CSC 17-1<br>COBIT 5 - EDM04.01\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Description\",\n                    \"visible\": false,\n                    \"minWidth\": \"600px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"\",\n                    \"html\": \"<h6>SD2.6 Code Review<\\/h6><b>Principle:<\\/b> A comprehensive review of the application code to identify any vulnerabilities introduced as a result of coding errors.<\\/br><b>Objective:<\\/b> To ensure any coding vulnerabilities that may exist in the code are remedied accordingly.\"\n                },\n                {\n                    \"type\": \"html\",\n                    \"name\": \"Frameworks\",\n                    \"visible\": false,\n                    \"width\": \"250px\",\n                    \"minWidth\": \"250px\",\n                    \"maxWidth\": \"250px\",\n                 